description: FIGURES 81–88. Calapnita subphyllicola Deeleman-Reinhold, left bulbal appendices, prolateral views. 81–84. Males from central Mindanao (81: Malagos, ZFMK Ar 16003; 82: Penolohan, ZFMK Ar 16007; 83–84: Santo Domingo, ZFMK Ar 16004–05). 85–88. Males from eastern Mindanao (85–86: Camp Abubakar, ZFMK Ar 16009; 87–88: Mount Mupo, ZFMK Ar 16010–11). Scale line: 0.2 mm (all at same scale).
name: FIGURES 81–88 in Revision and cladistic analysis of the Southeast Asian leaf-dwelling spider genus Calapnita Simon (Araneae, Pholcidae)
